{"tid":2152354,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張劍虹謝港人血肉衞《蘋果》","createTime":"2020-08-12T02:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T04:15:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0f29715ba7e1487be2c800e47a4aa0ac47525836","tid":2152354,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:49:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/ID7YYUT4RPHYAXPQJQJYGBNOPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FID7YYUT4RPHYAXPQJQJYGBNOPU%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=ad481641\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FID7YYUT4RPHYAXPQJQJYGBNOPU%2F&h=a0ab2800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/ID7YYUT4RPHYAXPQJQJYGBNOPU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n張劍虹謝港人血肉衞《蘋果》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/O4vVgIp-quqILWJyXleFvBoXquk=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JSJUVOS4E7VY37O35B56WELS4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FO4vVgIp-quqILWJyXleFvBoXquk%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJSJUVOS4E7VY37O35B56WELS4U.jpg&h=cbdfab9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n壹傳媒行政總裁張劍虹被扣留逾40小時後獲准保釋。許頌明攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方「810大搜捕」行動中，被捕人士有一半為壹傳媒高層，當中。。。。。。。。。。。。。並以史學家錢穆當年創作新亞校歌的其中兩句歌詞「艱險我奮進，困乏我多情」自勉，強調為理想不怕吃苦頭。<br />\n<br />\n張劍虹被指涉嫌觸犯港版國安法，前日早上7時許被捕，他先被帶往將軍澳工。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港人不值港府及警方所為，以「買爆」《蘋果日報》及股票作為「全民公投」表態，張被扣留期間，在警署與律師見面時獲悉《蘋果》昨創下開業以來最高的50萬份銷售數目，不忘感謝香港巿民「血肉長城保衞蘋果」，亦對香港人越打壓越反抗，感到「好感動，覺得香港人好可愛」，他有信心巿民熱情不會冷卻，寄語港人抱樂觀心態面對當前逆境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引新亞校歌：艱險我奮進<br />\n<br />\n1983年畢業於中大新聞及傳播學院的張劍虹，以校友身份引述新亞書院校歌其中兩。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，其餘多名壹傳媒高層昨晚陸續獲釋，營運總裁兼財務總裁周達權被扣留。。。。。。"},{"pid":"7064f7f52e93af8fe03d4b588f219a3f1a4e9a96","tid":2152354,"uid":54517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:15:32.000Z","msg":"香港人,可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}